headline: Bargain Income Powerhouses: These 2 Dividend Kings Could Deliver Massive Gains

headline: New Jeep Cherokee set to lead Stellantis' U.S. sales turnaround
summary: The Cherokee rejoins the compact and midsize vehicle markets after a three-year hiatus and will seek to compete with the Toyota and Honda hybrid vehicles.
